# World Happiness Dashboard

This web dashboard visualizes world happiness scores over time for different countries. It features a dropdown to select a country, displays a trend chart of happiness scores, and shows the latest happiness score in a colored card. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, utilizing Chart.js for chart rendering.

Usage:
Open `index.html` in a web browser. Select a country from the dropdown to see its happiness trend and current score.

Data:
Sample dataset embedded in the script. Replace with actual data as needed.

Dependencies:
- Chart.js library included via CDN.